edu.uta.cse.fireeye.common
Class TestSet

java.lang.Object
  edu.uta.cse.fireeye.common.TestSet

public class TestSet
extends java.lang.Object

A test set contains a list of parameters and a matrix of values in which each row represents a test. The parameter values in a test set are represented internally as an integer. These values need to be converted back to user-friendly values before they are displayed to the user. Class TestSetWrapper provides a number of methods for this conversion.
